#, no-c-format
msgid "SERIESSUM"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7243
#, no-c-format
msgid "The SERIESSUM() function returns the sum of a power series."
msgstr "Funktionen SERIESSUM() giver summen af en potens-serie."

