#, no-c-format
msgid "DEVSQ"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7833
#, no-c-format
msgid "The DEVSQ() function calculates the sum of squares of deviations."
msgstr "Funktionen DEVSQ() beregner kvadratsummen af afvigelser."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:7838
#, no-c-format
